latestPosts.caption:
Sometimes kids teach us so many things-
They just find joy in everything they see! ❤️
They are just content with everything they have!❤️
They are organic! Unapologetically themselves! ❤️

#love #joy #daughter #daughterlove❤️

Gone are the days of mothers competing with each other trying to proof and seek validation from places of insecurities and being pressured to raise kids with unrealistic expectations and unreasonable comparisons.

I now see a New Breed of Mothers who not only knows their self worth but knows how to champion each other, love their kids and celebrate each other’s win! 

Heart Talk - 
We Modern Mothers are often made to feel we are not as hardworking or efficient as our ancestors. Just a reminder that we don’t have our  Village with us all the time just the way they didn’t have diapers :) 
Let’s make our peace here and start appreciating the role of a mother who tried their best in the past and who is trying their best now. 
Next time you see a messy house and a dirty kid, don’t judge the mother but quietly lend a hand in cleaning the house, doing the dishes, cooking a meal, folding the clothes or washing the kid. 
Thank you. 💗

With that being said, 
It’s truly so cool and blessed to be a MOM! 💗

[ Moms Moments Captured at Zenei’s first birthday. The second born of @gracevvi ❤️ ] 
What a day it was!✨

#moms #momlife #blessing #momofinstagram
